-------open terminal--------
$ sudo systemctl start mongod
$ sudo systemctl status mongod
$ ls				#make sure you have a docker-compose.yaml file
$ docker-compose up

-------open a newtab---------
$ docker container ls		#Copy Mongo's container ID
$ docker exec -it [container ID] mongo -u root
>
>
>
> db				#shows which database you are currently on
> show dbs			#shows list of databases
> use [database_name]		#switch to database you want
> show collections		# shows collections/tables

